subject: Eclipse 3.2 RC2 supports JUnit 4
msgSnippet: All, JUnit 4 support has been built in to the public release of Eclipse 3.2 RC 2.  JUnit and Eclipse would both benefit from any testing you can do with your
messageBody:
All,

JUnit 4 support has been built in to the public release of Eclipse 3.2
RC 2. JUnit and Eclipse would both benefit from any testing you can do
with your own projects over the next couple weeks. Thanks,

David Saff
